1 create new repository
1.1 create local dir
1.2 cd this dir
1.3 git init
1.4 git  remote  add  origin  git://github.com/someone/another_project.git

2 comit
2.1 git add new_file
2.2 git commit new_file -m 'update'
2.3 git push

3 update
git pull

4 how to make push without typing username and password each time
bacause you use the https of push

git remote -v

git remote rm origin
git remote add origin git@github.com:youname/demo.git
git push origin

5 checkout
git clone git://github.com/youname/demo.git
or
git clone git@github.com:youname/demo.git

6 fix conflict 
http://www.01happy.com/git-resolve-conflicts/
